{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>React事件系统的事件被React团队称为合成事件，与浏览器原生DOM事件作区分， 用来声明和执行DOM事件。</p>\n<h2>如何运作</h2>\n<p>以一个onClick为例:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">EventApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'hello'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Click Here<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>用非JSX形式更形象的展现组件实例结构:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'div'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onClick</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hello'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'Click Here'</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>执行方法流程图相关部分：\n<img src=\"https://terry-su.github.io/CDN/images/how-react-works/how-react-event-system-works-1.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>在React的执行过程中，在一个DOM初始化属性时，如发现事件属性，则会绑定该事件。</p>","headings":[{"value":"如何运作","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/get-started/other-modules/how-react-event-system-works/cn/"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/get-started/other-modules/how-react-event-system-works/cn/","rootPath":"/cn/","locale":"zh_CN","decoratedLocale":"cn","texts":{"siteTitle":"React工作原理","getStarted":"开始使用","metaDesc":"React原理 React工作原理 如何实现React React源码","home":{"introduction":"了解React在底层如何运转"}},"pathname":"/cn/how-react-event-system-works","categories":[{"label":"整体流程","href":"/cn/whole-flow"},{"label":"Fiber","href":"/cn/fiber"},{"label":"模块","foldable":true,"folded":false,"items":[{"label":"JSX","href":"/cn/jsx"},{"label":"为什么setState是异步的","href":"/cn/why-setstate-is-async"},{"label":"React事件系统是如何运作的","href":"/cn/how-react-event-system-works"}]}]}}